             was indicted for <rs id="t18300708-170-off949" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300708-170-off949" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300708-170-off949" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
